Package: NordicPlantTraitExplorer
Type: Package
Title: Interactice shiny app for exploring Nordic plant traits
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Nora", "Fanebust",
      email = "nora.fanebust@hotmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: R package that launches an interactive shiny app for exploring relationships 
    among plant functional traits. The package includes a dataset of plant trait 
    values for over 3000 species from the Nordic region. Can visualise 
    trait relationships to explore ecological strategies such as leaf economics and rescouse useage.
